<subSubSection pageId="151" pageNumber="549" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="151.[1393,2599,1404,2266]" pageId="151" pageNumber="549">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1395,1754,2074,2107]" pageId="151" pageNumber="549">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Near Threatened on The IUCN Red List. Babault’s Mouse Shrew seems to have a very restricted distribution and is considered rare, although very little is known aboutit. Further research is needed.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
